{"sn1.40:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.40 ","sn1.40:0.2":"4. Satullapakayikavagga ","sn1.40:0.3":"Dutiyapajjunnadhitusuttam ","sn1.40:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","sn1.40:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava vesaliyam viharati mahavane kutagarasalayam. ","sn1.40:1.3":"Atha kho culakokanada pajjunnassa dhita abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanna kevalakappam mahavanam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. ","sn1.40:1.4":"Ekamantam thita kho sa devata culakokanada pajjunnassa dhita bhagavato santike ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn1.40:2.1":"“Idhagama vijjupabhasavanna, ","sn1.40:2.2":"Kokanada pajjunnassa dhita; ","sn1.40:2.3":"Buddhanca dhammanca namassamana, ","sn1.40:2.4":"Gathacima atthavati abhasi. ","sn1.40:3.1":"Bahunapi kho tam vibhajeyyam, ","sn1.40:3.2":"Pariyayena tadiso dhammo; ","sn1.40:3.3":"Sankhittamattham lapayissami, ","sn1.40:3.4":"Yavata me manasa pariyattam. ","sn1.40:4.1":"Papam na kayira vacasa manasa, ","sn1.40:4.2":"Kayena va kincana sabbaloke; ","sn1.40:4.3":"Kame pahaya satima sampajano, ","sn1.40:4.4":"Dukkham na sevetha anatthasamhitan”ti. ","sn1.40:4.5":"Satullapakayikavaggo catuttho. ","sn1.40:5.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn1.40:5.1":"Sabbhimaccharina sadhu, ","sn1.40:5.2":"na santujjhanasannino; ","sn1.40:5.3":"Saddha samayo sakalikam, ","sn1.40:5.4":"ubho pajjunnadhitaroti. "}